{"tid":169921,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"經常去歐洲既巴絲願唔願意俾2-3萬縮短3倍時間？","createTime":"2017-03-24T12:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T21:26:24.000Z","uid":17767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9514151ecb5bd77d1f48459fcce3e5a7b448e1b3","tid":169921,"uid":17767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fk49VAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFk49VAp.jpg&h=9044655b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n航空技術一直進步，過去風光一時的和諧式超音速客機雖然已經全部退役，不過超音速客機的概念仍然有人在追求。一家名為 Boom 的公司就準備重新推出超音速客機。<br />\n<br />\n在最近一個訪談中，Boom 的創辦人兼 CEO Blake Scholl就表示，雖然之前的和諧式客機因為耗油量太高和噪音問題而失敗，現在的新技術已經可以解決這些問題。他們打算首先推出 2.2 馬赫的 45 座位超音速客機，也就是比現時主流客機快 2.5 倍。而今年年底將會展出 XP1 超音速示範機，會是真正產品的 1/3 大小，以展示技術的可行性。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7azLkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7azLkb.jpg&h=7568f804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然是新公司，但 Boom 背後的人脈並不簡單，首先有維珍集團主席 Richard Branson 率先預訂價值 20 億的 10 架超音速飛機，也有眾多從航空界和科技界加盟的工程師和設計師，實力並不容小覷。當然，距離真正普及並降低成本至現時經濟客位的程度仍然非常遙遠，但多一個選擇，對消費者來說也是很歡迎的。"},{"pid":"190f4ff3d9debcdae1c2fd7ee1fd6e39423def14","tid":169921,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"當年就係太少人搭所以收皮"},{"pid":"929161a15be6f3624c599157e4ecbbe7bb3a8e29","tid":169921,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"一路都覺得和諧機好型棍"},{"pid":"a3bdefe9e73a2d038424e68a82a453c0eb9f1578","tid":169921,"uid":17767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年就係太少人搭所以收皮</blockquote><br />\n雖然協和號已經步入歷史，不過國外有消息指出2019年，協和號將有機會重出江湖！另外最近美國一家飛機製造公司宣佈，他們將打造出比協和號客機更快更便宜的超音速客機，不只紐約飛倫敦只要3小時24分，就連票價也只有協和客機的1/4！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/jmrkrp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fjmrkrp.html&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4d3eaa9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/jmrkrp.html</a>"},{"pid":"330c3c25c81b54c3049dc0c11d6b8a002dd65053","tid":169921,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"太貴<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"cf3378ce26046d509b93fd34d58c84d9d00200e9","tid":169921,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"今次可以玩到盡, 然後趕到9點鐘前番到公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3be526fd8cc48916023ec6e768c7967557c4ae","tid":169921,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BzB5xtGGsTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBzB5xtGGsTc&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bc3231b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BzB5xtGGsTc</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\ntarget平嘅客佢又食唔到，target business嘅客佢地又唔介意速度，寧願要舒適<br />\n倫敦夜晚上機，第朝去到紐約，舒舒服服，冇必要咁趕三個幾鐘"},{"pid":"46ebf539c0e9e31f6f909e94661577d2e2d1224b","tid":169921,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/BzB5xtGGsTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBzB5xtGGsTc&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bc3231b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BzB5xtGGsTc</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\ntarget平嘅客佢又食唔到，target business嘅客佢地又唔介意速度，寧願要舒適<br />\n倫敦夜晚上機，第朝去到紐約，舒舒服服，冇必要咁趕三個幾鐘</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n1QEj09Pe6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn1QEj09Pe6k&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9c5abc11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n1QEj09Pe6k</a><br />\n錯link"},{"pid":"2d7c55f38002e2658aa7408c2941d5249db2cae5","tid":169921,"uid":60183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:16:38.000Z","msg":"似運貨仲有機有市場"},{"pid":"fcdcf1fc48c628790bb0fe12a8748cfa4ba187ba","tid":169921,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:18:18.000Z","msg":"只為突破音障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21ac6dad427cf8d4132e86fc30cf11eeb50e96a","tid":169921,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:14:10.000Z","msg":"你應該問航空公司願唔願意"},{"pid":"6fd3257d92df4dadb572f756076970482a5ea68f","tid":169921,"uid":74120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:26:24.000Z","msg":"絕大部分既乘客，錢係最大考慮<br />\n只有好少好少既乘客，十個鐘同三個鐘差別會有影響<br />\n音速客機用既成本比起普通客機多好多，所以今日有科技唔得於做得住"}]}